msgid "Stop losing productivity on repetitive queries,Build your knowledge base, group solutions by topics to facilitate users."
msgstr "Stop losing productivity pada repetitive queries,Build Anda pengetahuan basis, group solutions oleh topik ke facilitate pengguna."

msgid "Enables admin to set N numbers of tickets for users to create and set N numbers of Ticket to open for agents separately."
msgstr "Memungkinkan admin menetapkan jumlah tiket yang dapat dibuat pengguna dan jumlah tiket terbuka untuk agen secara terpisah."

msgid "Enables agents to merge two tickets of the same user into one instead of dealing with the same issue on many tickets."
msgstr "Enables agen ke gabungkan two tiket sama pengguna into one instead dealing dengan sama masalah pada many tiket."

msgid "Defines rules or set specific intervals of time to make ticket auto overdue.The ticket can overdue by type or overdue by Cronjob."
msgstr "Tentukan aturan atau interval waktu tertentu agar tiket otomatis terlambat. Tiket dapat dibuat terlambat berdasarkan jenis atau Cron Job."

msgid "SMTP allows you to use a custom mail server to send emails from JS Help Desk."
msgstr "SMTP memungkinkan Anda menggunakan server email kustom untuk mengirim email dari JS Help Desk."

msgid "Displays complete ticket history along with the ticket status, currently assigned user and other actions performed on each ticket."
msgstr "Displays selesaikan tiket history along dengan tiket status, currently ditetapkan pengguna dan lainnya tindakan performed pada setiap tiket."

msgid "Canned Responses are pre-populated messages that allows support agents to respond quickly to customer issues."
msgstr "Respons tersimpan adalah pesan siap pakai yang membantu agen dukungan merespons masalah pelanggan dengan cepat."

msgid "Enables users to reply to the tickets via email without the need to login to the support system first."
msgstr "Enables pengguna ke balasan ke tiket via email tanpa need ke masuk ke dukungan sistem pertama."

msgid "Track the time spent on each ticket by each agent and each reply. Report the admin on how much time is spent on each ticket."
msgstr "Track waktu spent pada setiap tiket oleh setiap agen dan setiap balasan. laporan admin pada cara much waktu adalah spent pada setiap tiket."

msgid "User options enable you to add Google Re-captcha or JS Help Desk Re-captcha for a registration form."
msgstr "Pengguna options aktifkan Anda ke tambah Google Re-captcha atau JS Help Desk Re-captcha untuk pendaftaran formulir."

msgid "Get multiple action options on each ticket like Print Ticket, Lock Ticket, Transfer ticket, etc."
msgstr "Get multiple tindakan options pada setiap tiket like cetak tiket, Lock tiket, Transfer tiket, etc."

msgid "Make unlimited announcements associated with support system to get customer interaction."
msgstr "Buat pengumuman tanpa batas yang terhubung dengan sistem dukungan untuk meningkatkan interaksi pelanggan."

msgid "Ban Email allows you to block email of any user to restrict him to create new tickets."
msgstr "Blokir email allows Anda ke blokir email apa pun pengguna ke batasi him ke create baru tiket."

msgid "The Desktop notifications will keep you up to date about anything happens on your support system."
msgstr "Desktop notifications akan keep Anda up ke tanggal about anything happens pada Anda dukungan sistem."

msgid "Save the ticket as a PDF in your system or the admin will also be able to export all the data inside of Ticket."
msgstr "Simpan tiket sebagai PDF di sistem Anda, atau admin juga dapat mengekspor semua data di dalam tiket."

msgid "Create downloads to ensure the user to get downloads from downloads."
msgstr "Buat unduhan agar pengguna dapat memperoleh berkas dari bagian unduhan."

msgid "Tired of getting tickets about the same problems? Add FAQs to drastically reduce the number of common questions from users."
msgstr "Tired getting tiket about sama problems? tambah FAQ ke drastically reduce jumlah common questions dari pengguna."

msgid "Dashboard Widgets"
msgstr "Dashboard Widgets"

msgid "Get immediate data of your support operations as soon as you log into your WordPress administration area."
msgstr "Get immediate data Anda dukungan operations sebagai soon sebagai Anda log into Anda WordPress administration area."

msgid "Use internal email to send emails to one agent to another agent with in support ticket."
msgstr "Gunakan email internal untuk mengirim email dari satu agen ke agen lain di dalam tiket dukungan."

msgid "Widgets in WordPress allow you to add content and features in the widgetized areas of your theme."
msgstr "Widgets di WordPress izinkan Anda ke tambah konten dan features di widgetized areas Anda theme."

msgid "JS Help Desk WooCommerce provides the much-needed bridge between your WooCommerce store and the JS Help Desk."
msgstr "JS Help Desk WooCommerce provides much-needed bridge antara Anda WooCommerce store dan JS Help Desk."

msgid "Without a valid Envato license, clients will not be able to open a new ticket."
msgstr "Tanpa valid Envato license, clients akan tidak menjadi able ke buka baru tiket."

msgid "Adds the option to the registration form for prompting new users to subscribe to your email list."
msgstr "Adds option ke pendaftaran formulir untuk prompting baru pengguna ke subscribe ke Anda email daftar."

msgid "Paid Support is the easiest way to integrate and manage payments for your tickets."
msgstr "Dukungan berbayar adalah cara termudah untuk mengintegrasikan dan mengelola pembayaran untuk tiket Anda."

msgid "EDD offers customers to open new tickets just one click from their EDD account."
msgstr "EDD memungkinkan pelanggan membuka tiket baru hanya dengan satu klik dari akun EDD mereka."

msgid "It allows to create language-based email templates for all JS Help Desk email templates."
msgstr "Ini memungkinkan pembuatan templat email berbasis bahasa untuk semua templat email JS Help Desk."

msgid "CC(Carbon Copy) - the people who should know about the information which is being shared and the people included are able to see who is there in the list."
msgstr "CC (Carbon Copy) adalah orang-orang yang perlu mengetahui informasi yang dibagikan, dan penerima yang disertakan dapat melihat siapa saja yang ada dalam daftar."

msgid "It allows user to add more than one form based on requirements."
msgstr "It allows pengguna ke tambah lebih than one formulir based pada requirements."

